00:00:57.300 --> 00:01:03.700
♪How I crave a single reply♪

00:01:04.060 --> 00:01:08.660
♪Lonely souls are sand in the wind♪

00:01:09.260 --> 00:01:13.620
♪With nowhere to settle♪

00:01:13.980 --> 00:01:18.460
♪Broken all over, yet my heart won't give♪

00:01:19.020 --> 00:01:24.220
♪Like a flower blooming in a crack of stone♪

00:01:24.420 --> 00:01:28.980
[Loving Strangers]

00:01:29.020 --> 00:01:33.940
[Episode 9]

00:01:50.710 --> 00:01:51.210
Dad.

00:01:51.710 --> 00:01:52.290
Mom.

00:01:52.290 --> 00:01:53.950
[Late father Yao Youde; Late mother Chen Shulan]

00:01:53.950 --> 00:01:55.260
I'm not doing well.

00:01:56.590 --> 00:01:58.050
Dongshan isn't doing well either.

00:01:58.840 --> 00:02:01.210
Living really feels like suffering.

00:02:03.430 --> 00:02:05.020
Don't waste time. Kneel.

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:06.690
Kneel!

00:02:26.560 --> 00:02:27.450
I'm useless.

00:02:27.470 --> 00:02:29.130
I couldn't take good care of your son.

00:02:29.470 --> 00:02:30.690
If you're not happy,

00:02:30.690 --> 00:02:32.130
there's nothing I can do.

00:02:32.240 --> 00:02:34.080
Your daughter only has this much ability.

00:02:57.660 --> 00:02:58.290
Sis.

00:03:01.030 --> 00:03:01.730
Get in the car.

00:03:01.870 --> 00:03:02.290
No need.

00:03:02.310 --> 00:03:03.410
I'll go buy some groceries.

00:03:03.630 --> 00:03:04.730
You guys go back first.

00:03:05.080 --> 00:03:06.220
Mom, just come up.

00:03:07.360 --> 00:03:08.940
Keep doing your business.

00:03:26.800 --> 00:03:27.450
Mom.

00:03:29.000 --> 00:03:30.010
Next time you visit the grave,

00:03:30.030 --> 00:03:31.290
just let us know.

00:03:32.470 --> 00:03:33.610
We'll go with you.

00:03:34.310 --> 00:03:35.060
It's a long way,

00:03:35.240 --> 00:03:36.380
and your legs aren't so steady.

00:03:37.430 --> 00:03:38.290
I'm not crippled.

00:03:38.520 --> 00:03:39.380
I can walk on my own.

00:03:39.960 --> 00:03:41.380
Besides, it's a whole day.

00:03:41.430 --> 00:03:42.890
Won't it delay you from working?

00:03:57.120 --> 00:03:57.940
Heading out?

00:04:05.070 --> 00:04:05.610
Hello.

00:04:07.890 --> 00:04:08.610
I'm...

00:04:08.880 --> 00:04:09.900
the owner of Peterfu.

00:04:10.720 --> 00:04:11.330
It's you!

00:04:11.350 --> 00:04:12.050
- Jialu! - Jialu!

00:04:12.550 --> 00:04:13.370
Don't be rude!

00:04:16.190 --> 00:04:17.090
Easy.

00:04:18.920 --> 00:04:19.530
Ma'am,

00:04:19.960 --> 00:04:20.620
sorry.

00:04:21.960 --> 00:04:22.430
Sirs,

00:04:22.430 --> 00:04:23.020
sorry.

00:04:23.600 --> 00:04:24.290
It's all my fault.

00:04:24.480 --> 00:04:26.290
I didn't recognize the situation.

00:04:29.040 --> 00:04:30.330
So it looks like

00:04:31.230 --> 00:04:33.170
you've been asking around.

00:04:34.110 --> 00:04:34.900
Business's been bad

00:04:34.990 --> 00:04:35.900
for me recently.

00:04:36.230 --> 00:04:37.290
I'm really stressed out.

00:04:37.400 --> 00:04:38.820
So I acted impulsively

00:04:38.840 --> 00:04:40.060
and ended up doing something like that.

00:04:40.550 --> 00:04:41.820
Please forgive me.

00:04:44.600 --> 00:04:46.380
Don't be so formal.

00:04:46.990 --> 00:04:47.530
From now on,

00:04:47.530 --> 00:04:48.700
we're neighbors, after all.

00:04:50.990 --> 00:04:52.060
I've got my flaws too.

00:04:53.310 --> 00:04:54.380
Thanks, sir.

00:04:54.960 --> 00:04:55.700
Thanks, ma'am.

00:04:56.480 --> 00:04:57.060
Take this.

00:04:58.190 --> 00:04:58.850
Hey, no need!

00:05:06.660 --> 00:05:08.420
[Cefixime Capsules]

00:05:19.270 --> 00:05:20.810
You should only take one pill at a time.

00:05:23.600 --> 00:05:25.170
Why not go to the hospital instead?

00:05:26.680 --> 00:05:27.930
Working in PV

00:05:27.950 --> 00:05:28.900
and taking random medication?

00:05:30.310 --> 00:05:31.610
Don't make our dept look bad.

00:06:09.540 --> 00:06:12.780
[Gu Chen: Didn't you act sooner?]

00:06:13.340 --> 00:06:15.500
[Why's there no progress now?]

00:06:26.380 --> 00:06:28.060
[Zhe
Come out and see me.]

