Can you give your eyes a break?

00:06:58.480 --> 00:06:59.610
I need to practice drills

00:06:59.620 --> 00:07:00.460
and sell equipment

00:07:00.580 --> 00:07:01.460
to make money.

00:07:02.280 --> 00:07:03.940
If you hadn't saved me,

00:07:04.230 --> 00:07:05.850
you wouldn't have borrowed money from that guy.

00:07:06.350 --> 00:07:07.170
I have a share

00:07:07.640 --> 00:07:08.530
in the money you owe.

00:07:09.280 --> 00:07:11.020
I couldn't do it when I was at the company.

00:07:11.790 --> 00:07:13.020
You've been listening for so long.

00:07:13.190 --> 00:07:14.290
Haven't you found anything?

00:07:14.920 --> 00:07:15.500
Not even

00:07:15.520 --> 00:07:16.730
any suspicious detail?

00:07:19.110 --> 00:07:19.900
Don't even mention it.

00:07:20.400 --> 00:07:22.380
That person is just so boring.

00:07:22.560 --> 00:07:24.620
No leverage at work.

00:07:24.870 --> 00:07:25.900
Only one son,

00:07:25.990 --> 00:07:27.620
studying in Vancouver, Canada.

00:07:27.840 --> 00:07:28.730
The only dirt on him

00:07:28.750 --> 00:07:29.900
is his wife.

00:07:30.110 --> 00:07:30.970
But her affair

00:07:31.160 --> 00:07:32.410
is with your boss.

00:07:32.600 --> 00:07:33.500
Where else

00:07:33.520 --> 00:07:34.330
can I find dirt on him?

00:07:39.990 --> 00:07:41.060
So why'd you delete

00:07:41.080 --> 00:07:42.060
that photo?

00:07:42.670 --> 00:07:44.090
To catch you guys kissing,

00:07:44.430 --> 00:07:45.820
I didn't dare blink the whole way.

00:07:46.720 --> 00:07:47.820
I worked so hard.

00:07:48.190 --> 00:07:49.170
You just deleted it.

00:07:49.430 --> 00:07:50.210
Where else can we find

00:07:50.230 --> 00:07:51.290
such good evidence?

00:07:54.480 --> 00:07:55.290
I'm heading back.

00:08:06.480 --> 00:08:07.260
Congrats, Mr. Gu!

00:08:07.480 --> 00:08:08.970
- Congrats, Mr. Gu! - Congrats, Mr. Gu!

00:08:09.080 --> 00:08:09.580
Congrats!

00:08:13.160 --> 00:08:13.770
What's going on?

00:08:15.230 --> 00:08:16.580
Mr. Gu completed the report.

00:08:17.350 --> 00:08:19.090
The shareholders decided to invest more.

00:08:27.400 --> 00:08:28.730
All, stand up!

00:08:51.310 --> 00:08:51.980
Alright.

00:08:52.920 --> 00:08:54.020
You all worked hard too.

00:08:55.240 --> 00:08:55.930
Get back to work.

00:09:00.920 --> 00:09:03.260
First time I envy an outsourced employee.

00:09:06.040 --> 00:09:06.650
Cool!

00:09:07.760 --> 00:09:08.980
I've told you so many times.

00:09:09.880 --> 00:09:10.930
Work boldly,

00:09:11.190 --> 00:09:12.140
but stay humble in life.

00:09:13.710 --> 00:09:14.900
It's all about the atmosphere.

00:09:15.280 --> 00:09:15.930
Just once in a while.

00:09:17.040 --> 00:09:18.050
This is how I see it.

00:09:18.520 --> 00:09:19.260
The first

00:09:19.310 --> 00:09:21.740
is to let them see your strength.

00:09:22.190 --> 00:09:22.900
The second

00:09:23.710 --> 00:09:24.810
is to give those

00:09:24.920 --> 00:09:25.690
who are uncertain

00:09:25.830 --> 00:09:26.740
a clearer idea.

00:09:27.280 --> 00:09:28.930
Mr. Wang won't give up easily.

00:09:29.550 --> 00:09:30.020
The chairman

00:09:30.040 --> 00:09:31.290
has made his position clear.

00:09:31.360 --> 00:09:33.980
We need to accelerate the SA-0988 process.

00:09:34.360 --> 00:09:36.260
Now the situation is looking good.

00:09:36.670 --> 00:09:38.170
We must press on while we're ahead.

00:09:39.920 --> 00:09:40.900
The chairman's focused

00:09:40.920 --> 00:09:42.140
on the democratic vote.

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:44.140
He surely has his reasons.

00:09:44.710 --> 00:09:45.690
The more this happens,

00:09:45.830 --> 00:09:46.690
the more careful we need to be.

00:09:47.280 --> 00:09:48.170
We must respect

00:09:48.280 --> 00:09:49.450
the rules he set.

00:09:50.470 --> 00:09:51.570
If the Vice GM position

00:09:52.400 --> 00:09:54.100
is taken by Gu Chen,

00:09:55.240 --> 00:09:56.900
we'll be in a passive position

00:09:58.070 --> 00:09:59.260
for the re-election vote.

00:10:00.120 --> 00:10:01.220
So, we need to act fast.

00:10:01.310 --> 00:10:02.290
Among those directors,

00:10:02.310 --> 00:10:03.500
only three or four have the strength

00:10:03.830 --> 00:10:04.620
to fight for it.

00:10:04.880 --> 00:10:05.570
The only one

00:10:05.590 --> 00:10:06.620
who can stand with us,

00:10:07.310 --> 00:10:08.860
with the right qualifications

00:10:09.000 --> 00:10:10.290
and right ability,

00:10:10.470 --> 00:10:12.900
and who hasn't sided with Gu Chen yet,

00:10:13.070 --> 00:10:15.450
is Jiang Jiaqi.

00:10:18.950 --> 00:10:19.860
Leave it to me.

00:10:23.760 --> 00:10:24.860
[Clinical Phase Ⅲ Trial]
This was just sent to me

00:10:25.120 --> 00:10:26.020
[Extension Application Report]
by the R&D dept

00:10:26.040 --> 00:10:26.930
and PV.

00:10:27.040 --> 00:10:28.930
A Phase Ⅲ Trial Extension Application.

00:10:31.070 --> 00:10:32.770
Extension? Are they crazy?

00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:34.650
Leave it to me.

00:10:34.950 --> 00:10:35.570
Wait a moment.

00:10:36.920 --> 00:10:38.260
The chairman emphasized again

00:10:39.470 --> 00:10:40.740
that the approval process for market release

00:10:41.000 --> 00:10:41.770
must be flawless.

00:10:43.470 --> 00:10:44.120
Trying to change

00:10:44.120 --> 00:10:45.140
these researchers' minds

00:10:45.160 --> 00:10:45.980
is no easy task.

00:10:47.040 --> 00:10:48.170
Find another way.

00:10:49.120 --> 00:10:49.980
I'll think it over.

00:10:51.880 --> 00:10:53.380
I'll start entering it from here.

00:11:01.280 --> 00:11:02.690
Sen'an is a company.

00:11:03.280 --> 00:11:04.290
Don't you guys have

00:11:04.310 --> 00:11:05.140
even a basic sense of cost?

00:11:05.710 --> 00:11:06.980
If we extend the Phase Ⅲ trial

00:11:07.070 --> 00:11:08.740
according to your plan,

00:11:08.830 --> 00:11:09.570
it will increase costs

00:11:09.590 --> 00:11:10.620
by at least 8%!

00:11:10.920 --> 00:11:12.020
If safety issues

00:11:12.040 --> 00:11:13.650
delay the release of SA-0988,

00:11:13.710 --> 00:11:14.570
or worse, if problems arise

00:11:14.590 --> 00:11:15.340
after it's released,

00:11:15.760 --> 00:11:16.860
all the prior costs

00:11:16.880 --> 00:11:17.770
will go down the drain.

00:11:18.470 --> 00:11:20.050
You're acting like you're the only one

00:11:20.070 --> 00:11:21.380
worried about the company's drug safety.

00:11:21.520 --> 00:11:22.500
Have you asked

00:11:22.520 --> 00:11:23.570
other departments

00:11:23.590 --> 00:11:24.220
what they think

00:11:24.240 --> 00:11:24.770
about PV?

00:11:25.670 --> 00:11:27.290
You have no big-picture awareness!

00:11:27.640 --> 00:11:28.980
You're holding the company back!

00:11:29.280 --> 00:11:30.450
Don't you even

00:11:30.790 --> 00:11:31.690
realize this?

00:11:33.400 --> 00:11:34.530
Let me be clear.

00:11:35.000 --> 00:11:35.860
If you end up

00:11:35.880 --> 00:11:36.980
harming the company's interests,

00:11:37.470 --> 00:11:38.980
don't blame me for not warning you.

00:11:46.280 --> 00:11:46.740
Boss,

00:11:47.400 --> 00:11:47.980
should we

00:11:48.470 --> 00:11:49.140
change the plan?

00:11:49.710 --> 00:11:50.410
Our dept

00:11:50.470 --> 00:11:51.570
only does technical assessments.

00:12:10.160 --> 00:12:11.380
Mr. Gao is something else.

00:12:11.760 --> 00:12:12.810
He was just blowing up at Jiang

00:12:12.830 --> 00:12:13.690
in front of so many people.

00:12:13.710 --> 00:12:14.900
He didn't give Jiang any face at all.

00:12:15.520 --> 00:12:16.450
No matter what,

00:12:16.470 --> 00:12:17.380
Jiang has been working here

00:12:17.400 --> 00:12:18.570
for over ten years.

00:12:19.760 --> 00:12:21.620
But who's he really working for?

00:12:21.760 --> 00:12:22.530
Just look at his shifts

00:12:22.550 --> 00:12:23.650
these two years,

00:12:24.040 --> 00:12:26.450
moving from R&D to PV.

00:12:27.520 --> 00:12:28.380
Even though both are director positions,

00:12:28.470 --> 00:12:29.690
the difference between them

00:12:29.710 --> 00:12:30.690
is huge.

00:12:31.280 --> 00:12:31.740
So,

00:12:31.790 --> 00:12:32.860
his personal case

00:12:32.880 --> 00:12:33.290
is worth studying

00:12:33.310 --> 00:12:34.570
and we can learn a lesson from it.

00:12:34.920 --> 00:12:36.450
If you don't want to end up like him,

00:12:36.790 --> 00:12:37.570
don't repeat

00:12:37.830 --> 00:12:38.930
whatever he's done.

00:12:39.830 --> 00:12:41.020
Back in school,

00:12:41.040 --> 00:12:42.340
your junior used to suck up to you.

00:12:42.790 --> 00:12:44.100
And now he's your boss,

00:12:44.760 --> 00:12:46.260
and always trying to trip you up.

00:12:46.790 --> 00:12:47.690
Who wouldn't feel terrible?

00:12:48.040 --> 00:12:49.530
That's his problem.

00:12:49.950 --> 00:12:50.740
The workplace isn't where

00:12:50.790 --> 00:12:51.740
you find your emotional balance.

00:12:52.040 --> 00:12:52.930
When his junior

00:12:53.040 --> 00:12:54.500
becomes his superior,

00:12:54.550 --> 00:12:55.620
he should just walk away.

00:12:55.760 --> 00:12:56.650
He wouldn't have ended up

00:12:56.670 --> 00:12:57.290
in this situation,

00:12:57.310 --> 00:12:58.260
totally pinned down,

00:12:58.520 --> 00:12:59.770
and waiting

00:12:59.830 --> 00:13:00.740
to be kicked out.

00:14:15.070 --> 00:14:15.930
Zhiyuan...

00:14:18.310 --> 00:14:19.810
looks like I'm really getting old.

00:14:22.670 --> 00:14:23.380
Unlike you,

00:14:25.520 --> 00:14:26.860
always so young.

00:14:31.190 --> 00:14:32.140
My body feels like...

00:14:34.790 --> 00:14:36.570
it weighs a thousand pounds.

00:14:51.950 --> 00:14:53.770
Get up!

00:15:01.950 --> 00:15:02.690
Mom?

00:15:03.450 --> 00:15:04.690
Why didn't you knock?

00:15:07.160 --> 00:15:07.810
My son...

00:15:09.310 --> 00:15:11.020
why haven't you gotten married yet?

00:15:12.670 --> 00:15:13.980
Why did you guys

00:15:14.950 --> 00:15:16.290
end up in one bed?

00:15:18.160 --> 00:15:19.220
I fell down last night,

00:15:19.550 --> 00:15:20.810
and I couldn't be bothered to climb back up.

00:15:22.710 --> 00:15:23.290
Get up.

00:15:24.000 --> 00:15:24.530
Get up.

00:15:24.590 --> 00:15:24.930
Mom,

00:15:24.950 --> 00:15:25.930
you can't do this!

00:15:26.070 --> 00:15:26.620
Mom, you can't.

00:15:26.640 --> 00:15:27.340
One's my brother,

00:15:27.360 --> 00:15:28.170
and one's my son.

00:15:28.470 --> 00:15:29.450
When you both were young,

00:15:29.470 --> 00:15:30.570
I changed your diapers!

00:15:30.590 --> 00:15:31.020
Sis...

00:15:31.040 --> 00:15:31.810
What's there to be shy about?

00:15:31.830 --> 00:15:33.650
You know I'm almost fifty.

00:15:33.670 --> 00:15:34.930
Can you show some respect

00:15:35.070 --> 00:15:36.450
for a working person like me?

00:15:36.550 --> 00:15:37.260
What kind of working person

00:15:37.280 --> 00:15:38.020
sleeps in late

00:15:38.040 --> 00:15:39.290
at this hour?

00:15:39.710 --> 00:15:40.900
Hurry up and get to work.

00:15:41.310 --> 00:15:42.050
Jiaqi does

00:15:42.190 --> 00:15:43.810
both mental and physical work.

00:15:44.280 --> 00:15:46.050
Has he ever said he's tired?

00:15:46.400 --> 00:15:48.140
Now he's walking to work,

00:15:48.160 --> 00:15:49.650
full of energy.

00:15:50.040 --> 00:15:51.620
Don't blame me for being biased.

00:15:51.640 --> 00:15:53.260
You should learn from him!

00:16:06.360 --> 00:16:07.020
Jiaqi,

00:16:08.040 --> 00:16:09.530
your body weighs just 100 pounds.

00:16:10.430 --> 00:16:12.980
It's your heart feels like it weighs a thousand pounds.

00:16:24.760 --> 00:16:26.340
A perfect place for relaxation,

00:16:26.920 --> 00:16:29.220
a scenic retreat in the suburbs.

00:16:30.240 --> 00:16:31.570
Lia Resort,

00:16:31.950 --> 00:16:33.860
your natural oxygen bar,

00:16:34.830 --> 00:16:37.450
bringing your heart back to nature.

00:16:45.300 --> 00:16:47.140
[Chu Dan: Feeling refreshed now.]

00:17:27.360 --> 00:17:28.930
Even with your own pets,

00:17:29.510 --> 00:17:31.140
you wouldn't greet them with your feet, right?

00:17:48.230 --> 00:17:49.580
What job are you taking?

00:17:51.120 --> 00:17:51.820
We're hauling goods.

00:17:51.840 --> 00:17:52.930
Why are you ending up with a human model?

00:17:53.080 --> 00:17:53.780
A human model?

00:18:00.560 --> 00:18:01.340
What's wrong?

00:18:02.030 --> 00:18:02.620
Are you getting interested

00:18:02.640 --> 00:18:03.490
in a fake person?

00:18:03.710 --> 00:18:05.210
No, I just think she looks familiar.

00:18:10.950 --> 00:18:12.170
Enough.

00:18:14.030 --> 00:18:15.210
You need to get a girlfriend.

00:18:30.190 --> 00:18:31.170
Is it working or not?

00:18:34.950 --> 00:18:35.820
Why is delivering this stuff

00:18:35.840 --> 00:18:36.730
so troublesome?

00:18:36.920 --> 00:18:37.580
Such a small job,

00:18:37.600 --> 00:18:38.650
can't you do it by yourself?

00:18:38.670 --> 00:18:39.490
Why bring me?

00:18:41.230 --> 00:18:42.490
You're blaming me now?

00:18:42.950 --> 00:18:44.170
Go talk to the security.

00:18:44.670 --> 00:18:45.140
Who knew?

00:18:45.160 --> 00:18:46.160
He won't let the car in.

00:18:46.190 --> 00:18:47.250
Can't I carry it myself?

00:18:48.840 --> 00:18:49.930
You always cause trouble.

00:18:53.710 --> 00:18:54.170
Hello.

00:18:55.430 --> 00:18:55.900
Hi.

00:18:56.160 --> 00:18:57.340
We're the delivery team.

